chart.name: Sector 3 Time
chart.programText:
A = data('f1_2021.lastLapTime', filter=filter('driver', '*')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('f1_2021.sector1TimeInMS', filter=filter('driver', '*')).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = data('f1_2021.sector2TimeInMS', filter=filter('driver', '*')).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (A-((B/1000)+(C/1000))).publish(label='D')
